title: Vampirella Southern Gothic 003(2013)(Digital)(TLK-EMPIRE-HD).cbr
description: Stranded in the Deep South and severely wounded from a mystical demon's blade, Vampirella must continue her quest to save her former lover's soul, protect an innocent child, and not die in the process. Can Vampirella battle a bloodthirsty horde of rabid demons as her body fails her? It's sweaty vampire noir courtesy of NATE COSBY (Cow Boy, Buddy Cops) and Jose Luis (Bionic Man Vs. Bionic Woman)!
